data.description: Welcome home to this adorable 4 bedroom 2 bath home with many upgrades!  LVP flooring throughout main living area, living room has vaulted ceilings, open to formal dining room.  Kitchen has white cabinets, upgraded granite countertops, tile floors, smooth top stove-stainless steel, built in microwave, pantry.  Master suite is large with double vanity, garden tub & separate shower.  4th bedroom upstairs has been renovated and has large walk in closet.  Other amenities: HVAC-2019, fire pit, privacy fence, porch, security, and walk in attic.  Call us today for your personal tour!
